@startuml
[*] --> Order
state Order
state Arrival
state Preparation
state Operations
state Maintenance

Order --> Arrival : plane acquired
Arrival --> Preparation : plane arrived
Preparation --> Operations : plane prepared
Operations --> Maintenance : no scheduled flights
Maintenance --> Preparation : plane serviced

Order --> [*] : plane delivered
Arrival --> [*] : plane not available
Preparation --> [*] : plane not available
Operations --> [*] : plane not available
Maintenance --> [*] : plane not available

@enduml
